2012 public int ChildrenWeight
2013 {
2014 get
2015 {
2016 if (dirtyWeight)
2017 {
2018 _childrenWeight = 0;
2019 if (!(trait is TraitMagicChest))
2020 {
2021 foreach (Thing thing in things)
2022 {
2023 _childrenWeight += thing.ChildrenAndSelfWeight;
2024 }
2025 dirtyWeight = false;
2026 (parent as Card)?.SetDirtyWeight();
2027 if (isChara && IsPCFaction)
2028 {
2029 Chara.CalcBurden();
2030 }
2031 if (_childrenWeight < 0 || _childrenWeight > 10000000)
2032 {
2033 _childrenWeight = 10000000;
2034 }
2035 }
2036 }
2037 return _childrenWeight * Mathf.Max(100 - Evalue(404), 0) / 100;
2038 }
2039 }

3658 public bool CanAddRune(TraitMod mod)
3659 {
3660 SourceElement.Row source = mod.source;
3661 if (category.slot == 0)
3662 {
3663 return false;
3664 }
3665 if (material.HasEnc(source.id))
3666 {
3667 return false;
3668 }
3669 if (!IsWeapon && source.IsWeaponEnc)
3670 {
3671 return false;
3672 }
3673 if (source.category == "resist")
3674 {
3675 foreach (Element item in elements.ListElements())
3676 {
3677 if (item.source.category == "resist" && (item.vBase != 0 || item.vSource != 0))
3678 {
3679 return false;
3680 }
3681 }
3682 }
3683 string encSlot = source.encSlot;
3684 if (encSlot == null || encSlot.Length != 0)
3685 {
3686 switch (encSlot)
3687 {
3688 case "shield":
3689 if (!category.IsChildOf("shield") && !category.IsChildOf("martial"))
3690 {
3691 return false;
3692 }
3693 break;
3694 default:
3695 {
3696 bool flag = false;
3697 string[] array = source.encSlot.Split(',');
3698 foreach (string key in array)
3699 {
3700 if (EClass.sources.elements.alias[key].id == category.slot)
3701 {
3702 flag = true;
3703 }
3704 }
3705 if (!flag)
3706 {
3707 return false;
3708 }
3709 break;
3710 }
3711 case "global":
3712 case "all":
3713 case "weapon":
3714 break;
3715 }
3716 }
3717 if (mod is TraitRuneFree)
3718 {
3719 return true;
3720 }
3721 return CountRune(countFree: false) < MaxRune();
3722 }

5516 public Card MakeFoodFrom(Card c)
5517 {

5519 ChangeMaterial(c.material);
5520 if (!c.isChara)
5521 {
5522 return this;
5523 }

5544 }
5545 elements.SetBase(71, (int)Mathf.Clamp((float)(num / 10) + Mathf.Sqrt(race.height) - 10f, 1f, 60f));
5546 }
5547 else if (flag3)

5549 elements.SetBase(444, race.LER * race.LER / 5 * num / 100 - 10 + num / 10);
5550 num2 = 2;

5554 num2 = 3;
5555 }

5570 {
5571 elements.SetBase(value.id, value.Value);
5572 }

6458 public void CalculateFOV()
6459 {
6460 int radius = GetLightRadius();
6461 if (radius == 0 || !IsAliveInCurrentZone || !EClass._zone.isStarted)
6462 {
6463 return;
6464 }
6465 float power = GetLightPower();
6466 if (IsPC)
6467 {
6468 if (Chara.held != null && Chara.held.GetLightRadius() > 0)
6469 {
6470 power += Chara.held.GetLightPower();
6471 }
6472 if (radius <= 2)
6473 {
6474 power = 0f;
6475 }
6476 foreach (Condition condition in Chara.conditions)
6477 {
6478 condition.OnCalculateFov(fov, ref radius, ref power);
6479 }
6480 if (power > EClass.scene.profile.global.playerLightPowerLimit)
6481 {
6482 power = EClass.scene.profile.global.playerLightPowerLimit;
6483 }
6484 power *= EClass.scene.profile.light.playerLightMod + (float)EClass.player.customLightMod * EClass.scene.profile.light.playerLightCustomMod;
6485 EClass.player.lightRadius = radius;
6486 EClass.player.lightPower = power;
6487 }
6488 if (fov == null)
6489 {
6490 fov = CreateFov();
6491 }
6492 fov.Perform(pos.x, pos.z, radius, power * 2f);
6493 }

7155 public int GetValue(PriceType priceType = PriceType.Default, bool sell = false)

7178 num2 *= 0.5f;

7186 }

7189 else

7200 {
7201 num2 = Mathf.Max(num2, 1800f + num2 / 5f);

7203 num2 = num2 * (100f + num3 * (float)(material.value - 100)) / 100f;
7204 if (IsEquipmentOrRanged)
7205 {
7206 int num4 = 0;
7207 foreach (Element value in elements.dict.Values)
7208 {
7209 num4 += value.source.value;
7210 }
7211 num2 = num2 * (float)(100 + (sell ? ((int)MathF.Sqrt(num4) * 10) : num4)) / 100f;
7212 if (rarity >= Rarity.Legendary)

7216 }

7222 if (encLV != 0 && !category.tag.Contains("noEnc"))
7223 {
7224 num2 = (category.tag.Contains("enc") ? (num2 * (0.7f + (float)(encLV - 1) * 0.2f)) : ((!IsFood) ? (num2 * (1f + (float)encLV * 0.01f)) : ((!(id == "honey")) ? (num2 * Mathf.Min(1f + 0.1f * (float)encLV, 2f) + (float)(encLV * 100)) : (num2 + (float)(encLV * 10)))));
7225 }

7741 public virtual int SecondaryCompare(UIList.SortMode m, Card c)

7755 }

7757 {
7758 num = refVal - c.refVal;
7759 }

7761 {
7762 num = c_charges - c.c_charges;
7763 }
7764 if (num == 0)
7765 {
7766 num = encLV - c.encLV;
7767 }

7770 num = Num - c.Num;
7771 }
